### Register Device

This endpoint allows the registration of a new device with its specifications.

#### Request Body

- dimension (object)

    - length (number): Length of the device

    - breadth (number): Breadth of the device

    - unit (string): Unit of measurement

- isFrontCameraAvailable (boolean): Indicates if the front camera is available

- isBackCameraAvailable (boolean): Indicates if the back camera is available

- isWorking (boolean): Indicates if the device is in working condition

- active (boolean): Indicates if the device is active

- remarks (string): Additional remarks about the device


#### Response

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "statusCode": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "responseBody": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
